4Geeks Academy offers a 16-week AI Machine Learning Engineer course designed for beginners, with no prior experience required. Students will learn Python, SQL, Google Data Studio, and various machine learning algorithms. The course emphasizes hands-on practice in predictive modeling, supervised and unsupervised learning, and real-life problem-solving, preparing participants for roles in data-driven environments.

Classes are conducted thrice weekly with a maximum of 12 students, fostering an intimate learning atmosphere. Graduates receive certificates recognized by multiple organizations. Instruction is available in English and Spanish.

